## Copy Conventions
- **Titles**: Title case, no period.
- **Descriptions**: One sentence; start with outcome or type of work (e.g. “AI-powered…”, “Responsive…”).
- **Years**: “2024”, “2024 – Present”, or “2023” for past only.
- **Categories**: Use existing: Development, Design, Branding.

When adding a project, add it to both `Projects.tsx` (home grid) and `Work.tsx` (work page) with matching `id`, `title`, `category`, `description`, `image`, `year`, `link`, and `featured`/`status` if needed.
